section.section:
Any reimbursement from the Fund for applications approved on or after July 1, 1996 is subject to:
For owners or operators of six tanks or fewer, a deductible of $7,500;
For owners or operators of more than 6 but not more than 15 tanks, a deductible of $10,000;
For owners or operators of more than 15 but not more than 30 tanks, a deductible of $15,000;
For owners or operators of more than 30 tanks, a deductible of $20,000; and
For residential owners of heating oil tanks, a deductible of $500; and
